ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectMuskowekwan Band SETTING APART
PrecisSetting apart of 126.752 hectares (313.21 acres) of surface land, including mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the MUSKOWEKWAN BAND as Muskowekwan Indian Reserve N° 85-63, located in the Rural Municipality of Emerald N° 277 at approximately 4 kilometres from the Village of Bankend, Saskatchewan.
